      <ul>
          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="715337646">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-715337646" class="vote-count">326</span>
              <a id="btn-715337646" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="715337646">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mayday_anne/">Augentropfen</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/715337646">2013-08-14 20:47:06</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">早上和闺蜜打越洋电话又聊到王朔，挂上电话又找来他的海水火焰重读。我对火焰的喜爱已到癫狂状态，吴迪的死让我痛哭，脑海中不断重播她坐在池边的亭子里，晃荡着两条腿嗑瓜子的样子。如果我是张明，遇到吴迪这样的女生，然后她为我而死，我想我这辈子都不会再爱上别人了。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1049477/?comment_id=715337646"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
